        <span class="tip-icon" data-tippy-content="ðŸ’¡ Tip: Response times > 200ms may indicate: 1) Missing vector indexes on your Oracle tables, 2) Cold starts in Vertex AI, or 3) Network latency. Enable connection pooling and warm-up queries.">ðŸ’¡</span>
